\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jfn1665702577202.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jfn1665702577202.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jfn1665702577202.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jfn1665702577202\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $fieldname\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"jfn1665702577202___fieldname_264379\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the name of the current field or check for the presence of a specified field in the component.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"jfn1665702577202__topic_d83240e1_d83241e1_d83242e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jfn1665702577202__p_d83243e1_d83244e1_d83245e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldname</span> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code> }</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jfn1665702577202__topic_d55017e1_d55018e1_d55019e1_d55020e1_d55021e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d187963e75\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"jfn1665702577202__table_d8558e1_d8559e1_d8560e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jfn1665702577202__table_d8558e1_d8559e1_d8560e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jfn1665702577202__table_d8558e1_d8559e1_d8560e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jfn1665702577202__table_d8558e1_d8559e1_d8560e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jfn1665702577202__table_d8558e1_d8559e1_d8560e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jfn1665702577202__table_d8558e1_d8559e1_d8560e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jfn1665702577202__table_d8558e1_d8559e1_d8560e1__entry__3\">\n Name of a field. If omitted, the current field is used.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jfn1665702577202__topic_d55022e1_d55023e1_d55024e1_d55025e1_d55026e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d187963e129\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jfn1665702577202__p_d83252e1_d83253e1_d83254e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldname</span> returns:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jfn1665702577202__li_d34256e1_d34257e1_d34258e1\">Name of the current field if <var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var> is not specified. If there is no current field (that is, if the last node of the active path is not a field), <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldname</span> sets <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> to <code class=\"ph codeph\">-1101</code>.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jfn1665702577202__li_d34259e1_d34260e1_d34261e1\">Name of the field, if <var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var> is specified and the field is present in the component.\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jfn1665702577202__p_d83255e1_d83256e1_d83257e1\">If an error occurs <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains a negative value that identifies the exact error.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"jfn1665702577202__table_d8561e1_d8562e1_d8563e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following Field-Level ProcScript Functions</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jfn1665702577202__table_d8561e1_d8562e1_d8563e1__entry__1\">Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jfn1665702577202__table_d8561e1_d8562e1_d8563e1__entry__2\">\nError\nconstant\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jfn1665702577202__table_d8561e1_d8562e1_d8563e1__entry__3\">\nMeaning\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jfn1665702577202__table_d8561e1_d8562e1_d8563e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1101\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jfn1665702577202__table_d8561e1_d8562e1_d8563e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_FIELD&gt;\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jfn1665702577202__table_d8561e1_d8562e1_d8563e1__entry__3\">\nAn incorrect\nfield name was provided; either the field name is not valid syntactically\nor the field is not available in the component.\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jfn1665702577202__topic_d55027e1_d55028e1_d55029e1_d55030e1_d55031e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d187963e228\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jfn1665702577202__p_d83261e1_d83262e1_d83263e1\">Use in Form components.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"jfn1665702577202__note_w151ab1b7b9b5_w152ab1b7b9_w153ab1b7_w154ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> In Server Page, Service, and Report components, the last node of the\n            active path is never a field (the field never has focus). This means that\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldname</span> always sets <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> to\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">-1101</code>.</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jfn1665702577202__topic_d55032e1_d55033e1_d55034e1_d55035e1_d55036e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d187963e250\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jfn1665702577202__p_d83267e1_d83268e1_d83269e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldname</span> function is useful for writing global ProcScript that performs field-level actions.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jfn1665702577202__section_s13_4wy_zbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d187963e262\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldname</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">If you use a help message naming convention of <code class=\"ph codeph\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FieldName</var>_HLP</code>, you can use the following ProcScript\n               statement in the help trigger for the modeled field:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"jfn1665702577202__pre_uts_4wy_zbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger help\n help $text(\"%%$fieldname%%%_HLP\")\nend; help</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jnc1665702576977.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$entname</a><p>Return the name of the current entity or check for the existence of an entity in the component.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yga1665702577055.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$applname</a><p>Return the name of the Application Shell.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ksm1665702577277.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$instancename</a><p>Return the name of the current component instance.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528851\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528851\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$fieldname Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $fieldname Return the name of the current field or check for the presence of a specified field in the component. $fieldname { ( Field ) } Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Field String Name of a field. If omitted, the current field is used. Return Values $fieldname returns: Name of the current field if Field is not specified. If there is no current field (that is, if the last node of the active path is not a field), $fieldname sets $procerror to -1101 . Name of the field, if Field is specified and the field is present in the component. If an error occurs $procerror contains a negative value that identifies the exact error. Table 2. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following Field-Level ProcScript Functions Value Error constant Meaning -1101 <UPROCERR_FIELD> An incorrect field name was provided; either the field name is not valid syntactically or the field is not available in the component. Use Use in Form components. Note: In Server Page, Service, and Report components, the last node of the active path is never a field (the field never has focus). This means that $fieldname always sets $procerror to -1101 . Description The $fieldname function is useful for writing global ProcScript that performs field-level actions. Example: Using $fieldname If you use a help message naming convention of FieldName _HLP , you can use the following ProcScript statement in the help trigger for the modeled field: trigger help help $text(\"%%$fieldname%%%_HLP\") end; help Copy Related Links $entname Return the name of the current entity or check for the existence of an entity in the component. $applname Return the name of the Application Shell. $instancename Return the name of the current component instance. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}